window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The entire Aurora Chronicles in one book!</p> <p>Like Shadows in the Night</p> <p>Like Tears in Rain</p> <p>Like Lightning on a Wire</p> <p>Follow the saga of Ezekiel Aurora, a man that has built a reputation as one of the most reliable middle men in the criminal underworld. Using his quick wits, he uncovers a devastating secret that would shake the very pillars of the world, fights a deadly cyborg assassin, and goes on a rampage to protect those he loves.</p> <p>An action-packed tale filled with gritty streets, futuristic technology, and beautiful women, the Aurora Chronicles is for fans of Cyberpunk 2077 and Blade Runner.</p>"; 
